  "detailed_description": "Machorium - Muscle Aquarium Simulator - is a relaxing idle and sandbox game where you can unwind and have fun. <br>Use points generated by cute little decorative muscle men to unlock various items and create your ideal muscle aquarium, Machorium.<br><br>・Placing a macho in the aquarium generates macho points every second.<br>Feeding them their favorite protein generates additional points.<br>Enhance your favorite machos at the shop to increase the point generation rate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/aee635e463e8795615f398061a22051b.poster.avif?t=1769070562\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/aee635e463e8795615f398061a22051b.webm?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/aee635e463e8795615f398061a22051b.mp4?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Use accumulated points to unlock items in the shop to decorate your aquarium.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/e73e0afe9a857fb6a88b2cc0e0e3b43c.poster.avif?t=1769070562\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/e73e0afe9a857fb6a88b2cc0e0e3b43c.webm?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/e73e0afe9a857fb6a88b2cc0e0e3b43c.mp4?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Arrange the inside of the aquarium freely with unlocked items such as rocks, driftwood, aquatic plants, and decorations to create a comfortable environment for the muscle men.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/be85e5661987e992eacbdc6e9400e2b4.poster.avif?t=1769070562\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/be85e5661987e992eacbdc6e9400e2b4.webm?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/be85e5661987e992eacbdc6e9400e2b4.mp4?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Use the Picture-in-Picture feature to keep an eye on your favorite Machorium while working.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/de7adb10078253db885221ce44f7ab2e.poster.avif?t=1769070562\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/de7adb10078253db885221ce44f7ab2e.webm?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/de7adb10078253db885221ce44f7ab2e.mp4?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Spending time with your muscle men in your customized Machorium, enjoying the view at your own pace, will surely bring you relaxation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/5f251d417114b8c970d476f06677967e.poster.avif?t=1769070562\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/5f251d417114b8c970d476f06677967e.webm?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903660/extras/5f251d417114b8c970d476f06677967e.mp4?t=1769070562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
